trol with higher magnification of microglia morphology. Scale bars: 50 &#956;m.</p></caption><graphic xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" position="float" orientation="portrait" xlink:href="fvets-08-658344-g0001.jpg"/></fig><p>Additionally, due to a production error, the funding number for the funder APVV, was erroneously omitted. The missing number is &#8220;APVV-19-0193 (DC)&#8221;.</p><p>The publisher apologizes for these mistakes. The original article has been updated.</p></body></article></pmc-articleset>